Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.70,0:00:19.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,《比利小子》前情提要\N{\rYUANWEN}Previously on Billy the Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.91,0:00:22.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,凭什么一群富人就有权决定\N{\rYUANWEN}How come groups of rich men get to decide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么是对 什么是错\N{\rYUANWEN}what's right and what's wrong, Who lives and who dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这是对美国的背叛\N{\rYUANWEN}That's a betrayal of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.88,0:00:29.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们有消息说汤斯顿\N{\rYUANWEN}We have information that Tunstall
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:30.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想在这里开银行\N{\rYUANWEN}wants to open up a bank here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:32.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你俩要是不做点什么 阻止他成立银行\N{\rYUANWEN}If you two don't do something about closing that bank
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,阻止这个英国人做生意\N{\rYUANWEN}and stop this Englishman from running his store,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,卡特伦先生就只有\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Catron has no other option
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:40.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,把两位先生踢出群了\N{\rYUANWEN}than to remove you two gentlemen from the equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.39,0:00:41.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在给你本人\N{\rYUANWEN}You're an embarrassment to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:42.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和生意抹黑\N{\rYUANWEN}and to this business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:45.77,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来啊开枪啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Go on. Pull the trigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.94,0:00:51.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你永远不知道会下一个是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}You never know who could be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:53.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,找出来 因为我需要知道\N{\rYUANWEN}Find out 'cause I need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.69,0:00:57.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这个比利小子到底是谁 我该怎么终结他\N{\rYUANWEN}Who the hell is Billy the Kid? How can I get to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.32,0:00:58.78,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快快快 快走\N{\rYUANWEN}Go, go, go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:05.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那是德尔西亚娜 跟她在一起的是谁\N{\rYUANWEN}That's Dulcinea. Who's that with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:07.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我听说她订婚了 就要结婚\N{\rYUANWEN}I heard she's engaged to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:16.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,想跟我去别处坐吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You wanna come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.30,0:01:17.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-安娜  -爸爸\N{\rYUANWEN}Ana! - Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:20.01,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-付出代价  -把枪放下 老兄\N{\rYUANWEN}You pay. - Put that down, ol
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.72,0:01:23.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,只要我想 别说你女儿\N{\rYUANWEN}If I want it, I'll have my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:26.64,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,整个世界都任我鱼肉\N{\rYUANWEN}and not just with your daughter but with the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.73,0:01:29.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,无可争辩的是 我们已经卷入了与墨菲先生\N{\rYUANWEN}There is no hiding the fact that we are now effectively
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:31.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,和浩世公司的战争\N{\rYUANWEN}at war with Mr. Murphy and the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:34.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我最不想看到的 就是一场枪战\N{\rYUANWEN}The last thing I want is a shooting match,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:38.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但要是真到那一步 我们必须严阵以待\N{\rYUANWEN}but if it comes to it, we have to be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我知道汤斯顿在迪克·布鲁尔农场\N{\rYUANWEN}I know Tunstall keeps some of his stock
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:43.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,养了一批牲畜和牛\N{\rYUANWEN}down at Dick Brewer's ranch- his cattle and his horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:46.70,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-不如我们来场突袭  -突袭他们\N{\rYUANWEN}- I say we raid'em. - Raid'em
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯和他的部下都是职业杀手\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse Evans and his gang are all practiced killers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:52.79,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他们会觉得 干我们绰绰有余\N{\rYUANWEN}They gotta be thinkin' we're easy meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:56.00,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我真没想到你嘴里会说出这种话\N{\rYUANWEN}It's not exactly what I wanted to hear comin' from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这位是铅弹罗伯茨\N{\rYUANWEN}This here is Buckshot Roberts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.22,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们的人 他拔枪快狠准\N{\rYUANWEN}He's joined us. He's an amazing sharpshooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.30,0:02:01.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\rYUANWEN}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,汤姆·奥福利德 比利是我的偶像\N{\rYUANWEN}Tom O'Folliard. Billy's my hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:07.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我一路跑来投奔他\N{\rYUANWEN}I've come a long way to join his gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,杰西·埃文斯是个危险人物\N{\rYUANWEN}Jesse Evans is a real danger to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:13.90,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想问问你 能不能脱离墨菲\N{\rYUANWEN}I came to ask you if you'd stop working for Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他像魔鬼一样狡猾 杰西\N{\rYUANWEN}He's crooked as the Devil, Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:17.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,那你又是谁 大天使加百列吗\N{\rYUANWEN}And who are you? Fuckin' Archangel Gabriel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你都有什么发现\N{\rYUANWEN}What'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.85,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他得了天花 在维加斯的医院里\N{\rYUANWEN}He has smallpox. He's in a hospital in Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.23,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-很好 也许他要死了  -也许吧 也许不会\N{\rYUANWEN}- Great. Maybe he'll die. - Sur
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以呢\N{\rYUANWEN}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:03.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以 也许得有人去告诉他\N{\rYUANWEN}So perhaps someone should pay him a little visit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,生活的真相了\N{\rYUANWEN}and remind him of the facts of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:07.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我明白你意思\N{\rYUANWEN}I see what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:16.08,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我一直觉得生病时有人探望\N{\rYUANWEN}I always find it's nice to get some visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是件幸福的事\N{\rYUANWEN}when you're stuck in hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:21.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,或许可以给他来点鲜花\N{\rYUANWEN}Maybe time to bring some flowers or somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:24.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是天花\N{\rYUANWEN}It's smallpox.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,英雄所见略同\N{\rYUANWEN}Glad we agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.11,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-放那儿  -你好 警长\N{\rYUANWEN}Over there. - Howdy, Sheriff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.99,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有什么需要吗\N{\rYUANWEN}- Anything I can help ya with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.28,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不好意思 我是来关闭的这家非法银行的\N{\rYUANWEN}You see, I'm here to shut down this illegal bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\rYUANWEN}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你无权这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}You have no right to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:15.58,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反 我有一切权力这么做\N{\rYUANWEN}On the contrary. I have every right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:18.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-这是我的法定权力  -谁给你的\N{\rYUANWEN}This is my legal authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:21.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这些诉讼是由地检官托马斯·卡特伦\N{\rYUANWEN}These proceedings were instigated in a court
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:24.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,在圣达菲的地方法庭提出的\N{\rYUANWEN}in Santa Fe by District Attorney Thomas Catron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:27.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他碰巧也是卡特伦银行信托的老板\N{\rYUANWEN}Who also just happens to own Catron Bank and Trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你在扯淡吧\N{\rYUANWEN}This is bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布雷迪警长 我想正式告诉你\N{\rYUANWEN}Sheriff Brady, I wanna put this on record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:37.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不认为你在伸张正义\N{\rYUANWEN}I do not believe you are serving justice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也不认为你在为这里的人民服务\N{\rYUANWEN}or the ordinary people of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:42.19,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我觉得你在为浩世服务\N{\rYUANWEN}It looks like you're only working for the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:47.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,布鲁尔先生 作为执法人员\N{\rYUANWEN}Mr. Brewer, my reputation as a law officer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我的声誉不容玷污\N{\rYUANWEN}is pretty spotless.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:51.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我两不偏袒 我的工作很简单\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't show favoritism. My job is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:54.62,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我维护法律\N{\rYUANWEN}I uphold the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,日安 我们走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Good day. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:09.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想让我射中前面的罐子\N{\rYUANWEN}You want me to try and hit those there things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我连看见都费劲儿  -像这样啦\N{\rYUANWEN}- I can't hardly see'em. - It'
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你多久练习一次\N{\rYUANWEN}How often do you practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.94,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你每天都要练习\N{\rYUANWEN}You gotta practice every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你得勤学苦练 这样枪才会长在你手上\N{\rYUANWEN}You got to work at it, so the gun just becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,弹指之间 百发百中\N{\rYUANWEN}an extension of your hand just like pointing your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:32.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 这需要时间\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, hey, well, that's gonna take...time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你时间不多了\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, you ain't got much time, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一场大战就在眼前\N{\rYUANWEN}This thing's about to get real messy real quick,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:40.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以你要么练习 要么进步 要么走人\N{\rYUANWEN}so you either practice, you work at it, or you Ieave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:42.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不会走的\N{\rYUANWEN}I ain't leavin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:43.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我跟定你俩了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm with you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.63,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你左手也能开枪 对吧\N{\rYUANWEN}You can fire with your left hand too, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这我一辈子也赶不上\N{\rYUANWEN}I ain't never gonna be able to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也不行 汤姆\N{\rYUANWEN}No. Me neither, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:28.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来吧 把他们赶到一起\N{\rYUANWEN}Come on. Let's gather em up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:41.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,嘿 滚出我的地盘\N{\rYUANWEN}Hey! Get off my property!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:46.61,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,快走 滚出去\N{\rYUANWEN}Let's go! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:08:00.12,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这些都是我的马 你们这群偷马贼\N{\rYUANWEN}They're my horses, you goddamn thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.67,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,狗娘养的\N{\rYUANWEN}Son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-嘿 比利  -吁\N{\rYUANWEN}- Hello, Billy. Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.45,0:08:36.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你好啊\N{\rYUANWEN}Hola.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,来 让我来吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Here, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.05,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.72,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 你怎么了\N{\rYUANWEN}Okay, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:03.27,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不懂 你怎么这么安静\N{\rYUANWEN}I don't understand. Why are you so quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:10.81,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我前几天在城里 见你跟一个男人在一起\N{\rYUANWEN}I saw you in town the other day with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:14.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你看起来很爱他的样子\N{\rYUANWEN}Sure looked like you were in love with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我当然爱他\N{\rYUANWEN}Of course I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.16,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是我哥哥\N{\rYUANWEN}He's my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,难道我不该爱我哥\N{\rYUANWEN}Am I not supposed to love my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.75,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,有人说你订婚了 就要结婚了\N{\rYUANWEN}Someone said you're engaged to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:37.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不假\N{\rYUANWEN}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:44.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我小时候 婚姻就被我爸包办了\N{\rYUANWEN}My father arranged my marriage while I was still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.47,0:09:48.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,与西班牙某位豪门长子联姻\N{\rYUANWEN}A good marriage with the eldest son of a rich Spanish family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.36,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们明年就该结婚的\N{\rYUANWEN}We're supposed to get married next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:58.15,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-我从未见过他  -真是荒唐\N{\rYUANWEN}- I have never met him. That'
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你应该嫁给自己想嫁的人\N{\rYUANWEN}You should be able to marry whoever the hell you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:02.24,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你不明白\N{\rYUANWEN}You don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:04.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我要是违抗父命 自己的\N{\rYUANWEN}I could lose my future,
