Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.33,0:40:42.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,行\N{\rYUANWEN}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.38,0:40:46.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这样我们也不欠你的了\N{\rYUANWEN}Now we got this tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.34,0:40:48.17,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们把马带走\N{\rYUANWEN}We take the horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.21,0:40:50.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,然后分道扬镳 好吧\N{\rYUANWEN}Then we split. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.38,0:40:52.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,-对  -没错\N{\rYUANWEN}Right. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.38,0:40:56.35,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你现在会跟莱利怎么说\N{\rYUANWEN}What you gonna say to Riley now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.47,0:40:59.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会告诉他 这场仗是我们赢了 贝克\N{\rYUANWEN}Well, I'm gonna tell him that we're winning the war, Baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.27,0:41:02.31,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你会怎么跟他说\N{\rYUANWEN}What are you gonna tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.39,0:41:04.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好了 伙计们 走吧\N{\rYUANWEN}AII right, boys, let's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.65,0:41:07.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,大家都吃过早餐了\N{\rYUANWEN}We've had our breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.29,0:41:25.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\rYUANWEN}Goddamnit! -
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.26,0:41:31.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\rYUANWEN}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.35,0:41:41.10,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你现在可以进去了\N{\rYUANWEN}You can go in now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.78,0:41:59.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你有个儿子 查理\N{\rYUANWEN}You have a son, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.28,0:42:01.29,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,儿子 你确定吗\N{\rYUANWEN}A son? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.41,0:42:03.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.87,0:42:09.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想抱抱他吗\N{\rYUANWEN}You want to hold him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.63,0:42:11.21,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我可以抱吗\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.30,0:42:13.26,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\rYUANWEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.38,0:42:15.76,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他也是你的儿子\N{\rYUANWEN}He's yours, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.81,0:42:30.65,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他真美了\N{\rYUANWEN}He's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.36,0:42:38.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你想叫他什么名字\N{\rYUANWEN}What do you want to call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.45,0:42:44.20,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你不介意的话\N{\rYUANWEN}If it's all right with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.29,0:42:46.33,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想叫他比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I'd like to call him Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.21,0:42:50.25,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我太高兴了\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.34,0:42:53.09,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,可我很害怕\N{\rYUANWEN}And I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.42,0:42:58.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,别担心\N{\rYUANWEN}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.55,0:43:01.18,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\N{\rYUANWEN}Everything will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.43,0:43:06.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我爱你 查理\N{\rYUANWEN}I love you, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.64,0:43:10.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,闭上眼睛\N{\rYUANWEN}Close your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.52,0:43:13.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,睡一觉\N{\rYUANWEN}Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.33,0:44:08.87,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,朋友们\N{\rYUANWEN}Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.96,0:44:12.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,麦克斯温太太 威尔逊法官\N{\rYUANWEN}Mrs. McSween. Judge Wilson.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.92,0:44:14.88,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,先生们\N{\rYUANWEN}Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.47,0:44:22.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们试过了\N{\rYUANWEN}We tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.34,0:44:24.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这才是最重要的\N{\rYUANWEN}That's the main thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.47,0:44:25.80,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想过争取和平\N{\rYUANWEN}I wanted to bring peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.89,0:44:28.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想过避免战争\N{\rYUANWEN}I wanted to avoid war.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.43,0:44:32.60,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,不幸的是 对方不想要和平\N{\rYUANWEN}Unfortunately, the other side doesn't want peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.69,0:44:37.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,好吧 那就让战争开始吧\N{\rYUANWEN}AII right then, this is war. So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.48,0:44:45.32,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我有最优秀 最诚实 最正派的人站在我身边\N{\rYUANWEN}I have the best, most honest, and decent people around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.41,0:44:47.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果战斗不可避免 我们就全力以赴\N{\rYUANWEN}If we have to fight, we have to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.91,0:44:50.50,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这就是我们的风格\N{\rYUANWEN}That's the way things get done out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.62,0:44:53.37,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我不是傻瓜 我知道敌人有多强大\N{\rYUANWEN}I'm not a fool. I knew what I was taking on,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.46,0:44:56.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我也不会临阵脱逃\N{\rYUANWEN}and I am not running away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.96,0:45:01.34,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,所以让我们“大闹一场 杀他个痛快”\N{\rYUANWEN}So let's"cry havoc and let slip the dogs of war, "
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.42,0:45:03.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,正如莎士比亚所说\N{\rYUANWEN}as Shakespeare put it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.38,0:45:06.30,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,毫无疑问\N{\rYUANWEN}And I have no doubt, no doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.39,0:45:08.97,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将取得胜利\N{\rYUANWEN}that we shall emerge victorious,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.06,0:45:13.98,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我们将一起把浩世夷为平地\N{\rYUANWEN}and that we together will take the House down.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.06,0:45:15.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\rYUANWEN}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.06,0:45:18.57,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,朋友们 让我们为此举杯\N{\rYUANWEN}My friends, let us drink to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.73,0:45:23.40,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,让我们\N{\rYUANWEN}Let us drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.49,0:45:24.66,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,喝下胜利\N{\rYUANWEN}...to victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.66,0:45:30.83,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,干杯\N{\rYUANWEN}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.50,0:45:41.38,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\rYUANWEN}Billy
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.46,0:45:43.51,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我想向你道歉\N{\rYUANWEN}I want to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.59,0:45:47.39,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我逼着你执行我的荒唐计划\N{\rYUANWEN}I forced you to support my ridiculous plan
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.47,0:45:50.47,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,甚至都没跟你解释原因\N{\rYUANWEN}without even having the decency to explain things to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.56,0:45:51.89,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,什么原因\N{\rYUANWEN}What things?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.98,0:45:56.02,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我在住院时 有人来看望我\N{\rYUANWEN}While I was in the hospital, I was visited by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.10,0:45:59.44,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他是生意里的一位重量级玩家\N{\rYUANWEN}a significant player in this whole business,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.52,0:46:01.82,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,他告诉我 如果继续跟浩世斗下去\N{\rYUANWEN}who told that me that if I continued my war
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.90,0:46:07.49,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我会死得很难看\N{\rYUANWEN}against the House, I would be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.57,0:46:08.91,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我慌了神\N{\rYUANWEN}I panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.99,0:46:11.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我失去了勇气\N{\rYUANWEN}My courage deserted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.66,0:46:14.71,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你又是怎么找回勇气的\N{\rYUANWEN}Hmm. How come you've rediscovered it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.83,0:46:17.54,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,逼你参与我的愚蠢计划\N{\rYUANWEN}By forcing you to go along with my stupid plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.63,0:46:19.42,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我差点害你被杀\N{\rYUANWEN}I nearly got you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.50,0:46:21.84,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,但你明知自己有危险\N{\rYUANWEN}But you were prepared to stand up for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.92,0:46:24.59,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,也愿意为我挺身而出\N{\rYUANWEN}even though you knew the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.67,0:46:27.93,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,是我对不起你 比利\N{\rYUANWEN}I owe you a great deal, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.01,0:46:31.56,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,你向我展示了友谊的价值和力量\N{\rYUANWEN}You reminded me of the value and the power
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.68,0:46:36.73,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,我永远都欠你一份情\N{\rYUANWEN}of true friendship, and I will forever be in your debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.81,0:46:40.48,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,这也是从莎士比亚里抄的吗 汤斯顿先生\N{\rYUANWEN}Is that from Shakespeare, too, Mr. Tunstall?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.69,0:46:46.45,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你想让我做你的合伙人\N{\rYUANWEN}If you want me to be a partner in this,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.57,0:46:51.07,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,如果你想取得胜利 就必须相信我\N{\rYUANWEN}if you want to be victorious, you need to trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.16,0:46:52.95,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,战争呼之欲出 我们的目标是赢\N{\rYUANWEN}We have a war to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.58,0:46:56.41,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,从明天开始\N{\rYUANWEN}It starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.75,0:47:01.96,YIWEN,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\rYUANWEN}Thank you.
